item.description: Have you ever had an appointment with a doctor and he says he can't find anything but you know you have something wrong? How about you have a trauma of some kind and then a mysterious pain shows up somewhere in your body and there is no explanation but it is correlates to the exact time of the incident. Our bodies are made of energy and it holds vibrations. Some vibrations create comfort and some vibrations create pain. In this movie we will learn about the mental causes for the physical illness and the metaphysical ways to overcome them. We will talk about the problem, the probable causes and the affirmation to create a new thought pattern.

group.name: Abundance, Empowerment and the Law of Attraction
